                <div class="content">
                    <div class="content-text">
                        <p>
                            Enjoy Minnesota summers with a custom-built deck,
                            patio, or outdoor feature designed for the way you
                            live. As local deck builders, we create durable
                            outdoor spaces that bring your home and yard
                            together.
                        </p>
                        <div class="picture">
                            <img src="/assets/img/services/decks/deck1.webp" alt="Custom Deck Renovation">
                            <div class="caption">
                                Custom Deck Renovation
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <br>
                        <div class="picture">
                            <img src="/assets/img/services/decks/38.jpg" alt="Custom Deck Renovation">
                            <div class="caption">
                                Custom Deck Renovation
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <br>
                        <div class="picture">
                            <img src="/assets/img/services/decks/29.jpg" alt="Custom Deck Renovation">
                            <div class="caption">
                                Custom Deck Renovation
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <Footer />
